features: COMPLETE CLOSET ORGANIZER—organize by size/age with 60 durable plastic baby clothes hangers and 6 baby clothing dividers — great for children’s jackets, pants, shirts, dresses, and more.
TOUGH & DURABLE PLASTIC HANGERS—gentle on little garments, these plastic hangers measure 11.42 x 6.5 x 1/5 inches and are made to maximize closet space and keep items organized.

ADORABLE LABELED DIVIDERS— cute animal prints look great and are divided into 0-3, 3-6, 6-9, 9-12, 12-18, and 18-24 months to help you create organized sections; dividers are durable plastic with a double-sided design that easily surrounds your closet rod.

STANDARD DIVIDER SIZE TO FIT ALL CLOSETS—clothing dividers measure 3 1/2 inches with an inside diameter of 1 3/8 inches and a thickness of 1/8 inch. Fits around a standard 1.25'' or smaller diameter closet rod.
CLOTHES STAY PUT— no-slip design, features notched shoulders to help prevent clothes from slipping or falling off.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great start up hangers for first baby
